Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

Class Model

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain.Model
public class Model extends Object
Author:
Leo Gaynor: 300437633

The Model Class Provides a centralized place for all essential parts of the game state. It provides methods for getting various parts of the game logic, and calls win and loss methods.
